{"tid":1463640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[理性啲大家]支那有十三億人，我地捉唔晒十三億隻鬼架","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:56.000Z","uid":110105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4410580db4f3dd04c2fa63f701d3c09aec7efd50","tid":1463640,"uid":110105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"唔好再沉迷捉鬼<br />\n你捉一隻，佢派返一隻落黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就喺度空轉左一晚</span><br />\n捉鬼冇意義架<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記雨傘點樣消亡<br />\n承認有鬼呢個事實<br />\n鬼肯定唔係第一日入黎<br />\n而612已經過左兩個月啦<br />\n咁多次行動有邊次真係因為鬼而壞事？<br />\n<br />\n做返應該做既野啦咁多位手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a909418a8183661d08d42f8beb8b3660cf6e40","tid":1463640,"uid":110105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105e80fb7b379bd6114d4240a93fa623bd907c71","tid":1463640,"uid":110105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4d35722db877b5134ec41875aadbf31c6e8a28","tid":1463640,"uid":110105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100c5dc5c4df9a9b4b343534109200139c443677","tid":1463640,"uid":110105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gi